  %p
    Inspired by the awesome MakeyMakey (<a href='http://makeymakey.com'>http://makeymakey.com</a>), this GPIO driver allows you to connect a 10 MOhm resistor to a digital pin on your Arduino or Raspberry Pi to control your robots with bananas, clay, or drawable circuitry.


